    Sign In or Create a Shop Account

    Welcome to the Dunkin' Donuts Online Shop! You can create a separate account for online shopping. Through this separate account, you'll be able to opt-in for email communications and set up payment options just for online shopping. Please note that your email communication preferences and DD Card reload / auto recharge information, if you have already set those up on DunkinDonuts.com, are not impacted by your online shopping account. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact our Customer Service team at 877-833-2633 (877-8DD-COFFEE). Happy Shopping!
